articles.title: Website Still In Progress!
articles.description: I'm not entirely sure what I'll do with this website. Perhaps I'll rename this section from "About" to "Projects," and then I will add some small projects that'll include R code, graphics, and some commentary. Nothing too fancy and nothing not not fancy... amazing English.

            Nathan Nguyen
          
          
            
              I just graduated with a bachelor’s of science in mathematics, and I have experience with statistical modeling with my main tool being R. I’m currently a volunteer research assistant at Valleywise Health Medical center where I help with internal research projects e.g., reports, models, and hypothesis testing. My career interests are in the realm of public health.
